data.description: Indulge in the charm of this 4-bed farmhouse on a corner lot. The open kitchen, with an island and SS apron sink, seamlessly connects to the living and dining areas. Durable vinyl plank flooring ensures style and resilience, ideal for kids and pets. The master bedroom boasts a spa-like bathroom, double vanities, a soaker tub, and a sizable closet. Secondary bedrooms offer comfort with walk-in closets, and a generous hall bath accommodates a large family. The utility area fits a full-size washer and dryer, accompanied by a mud bench. Two wood decks, front and back, extend living spaces. With an acre of land, there's ample room for kids to play. The side driveway, third entrance, and a shed at the end add practicality. Consider a front circle drive for enhanced curb appeal. Explore the thoughtfully designed spaces, envisioning a life of style and comfort. Schedule a viewing and make this dream home yours. Welcome home!
